{"tid":2374190,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小米旗下 POCO 以獨立品牌進軍台灣市場，推出最低不到 4 千元的超值機種 POCO M3","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T09:54:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f11bd1ef6bc2422faccff9eb41eef5d1c892d656","tid":2374190,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"小米在 2018 年為了擴充中國以外海外市場產品布局，於印度推出 Pocophone 品牌與 Pocophone F1 ，也在當時引進台灣以媲美小米旗艦機的性能、更便宜的價格受到關注，後續品牌名稱簡化為 POCO ，而今日小米台灣宣布 POCO 將以獨立子品牌的身分進軍市場，首發搭載高通 Snapdragon 662 的平價 4G 機種 POCO M3 。▲ 64GB 版本不到 4,000▲ 128GB 再多 700 元▲早鳥加贈行動電源POCO M3 提供動力黑、冷酷藍與活力黃三色，提供 4GB RAM 搭配 64GB 儲存與 4GB RAM 搭配 128GB 兩種配置，建議售價 3,999...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/159390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F159390&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=6d89a518\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/159390</a>"},{"pid":"71e2c4f80c5e03825f4feb0ec125b5b46ce465e0","tid":2374190,"uid":80866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"小米由低價品牌變左高價，開多條賤價brand<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff61f072f9b33395d4b68e3692826d8b89396adc","tid":2374190,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"M3禁飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c110874318139e9153ada10734554497b04521","tid":2374190,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"乜佢仲有晶片咩？"},{"pid":"5c17abfb3115907f2add284ded7cf6056a2db965","tid":2374190,"uid":257491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3c110874318139e9153ada10734554497b04521","tid":2374190,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"乜佢仲有晶片咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:47:50.000